<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<title><%= @shout.jumbo_name %>'s score</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/text.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/960.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
<style>
li {
color: #09a7e2;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
	<div class="container_12">
		<div class="grid_12">
			<div class="grid_3">
			<img src="/img/logo_lg.png" alt="mumbojumbo" />
			</div>
			<!-- end .grid_3 -->
			<div class="grid_6">
			<div style="margin-top: 30px;"
			<a href="/"><img src="/img/logo_txt_lg.png" alt="mumbojumbo" /></a>
			<h2>A game to help you communicate.</h2>
			</div>
			</div>
			<!-- end .grid_6 -->
			<div class="clear"></div>
			<img src="/img/header_border.png">
		</div>
		<!-- end .grid_12 -->
		<div class="clear"></div>
		<div class="grid_8">
			<div class="main">
			<span style="text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;">
			<p><span style="font-size: 2.5em; font-weight: bold;">Hello</span><br />
			<span style="font-size: 1.6em; 	word-spacing: .2em;">My Name Is</span></p>
			<h3 class="user_name"><%=h @shout.jumbo_name %></h3>
			</span>
			</div>		
					<div class="ratings">
					<div class="grid_2 alpha">
					<img src="/img/clarity_icon.png" alt="Clarity">
					</div>
					<div class="grid_4 prefix_1">
					<img src="/img/clarity_text.png" alt="Clarity"> <br />
					Mumbo knows that you aren't impressing anyone with all those big words, and your're probably not getting your point across, either.<li>You used about <%=h @shout.letters_per_word  %> letters per word</li>
					</div>
					<div class="grid_1 omega">
					<div class="score">
					<%=h @shout.clarity_score %>
					</div>
					</div>
														<div class="clear"></div>

					</div>
					
										<div class="clear"></div>
										<div class="sep"></div>


					
					<div class="ratings">
					<div class="grid_2 alpha">
					<img src="/img/brevity_icon.png" alt="Brevity">
					</div>
					<div class="grid_4 prefix_1">
					<img src="/img/brevity_text.png" alt="Brevity"> <br />
					What's your point already? Your brevity score measures your ability to 'spit it out already' by averageing your words per sentence.
					<li>You used about <%=h @shout.words_per_sentence %> words per sentence</li>
					</div>
					<div class="grid_1 omega">
					<div class="score">
					<%=h @shout.brevity_score %>
					</div>
					</div>
														<div class="clear"></div>

					</div>
					
									<div class="clear"></div>
														<div class="sep"></div>

					
					<div class="ratings">
					<div class="grid_2 alpha">
					<img src="/img/accuracy_icon.png" alt="Accuracy"> 
					</div>
					<div class="grid_4 prefix_1">
					<img src="/img/accuracy_text.png" alt="Accuracy"> <br />
					When you have a good product, you don't have to over-sell it.  There's an easy way to determine if you're over-doing it: add up your superlatives.
					<li>You used <%=h @shout.superlatives  %>
					<% if @shout.superlatives == 1 %> superlative 					
					<% else %> superlatives
					<% end %>
					</li>
					</div>
					<div class="grid_1 omega">
					<div class="score">
					<%=h @shout.accuracy_score %>
					</div>
					</div>
														<div class="clear"></div>

					</div>
					
					<div class="clear"></div>
					<div class="sep"></div>
					
					<div class="ratings">
						<div class="grid_2 alpha">
							<img src="/img/reach_icon.png" alt="Reach">
						</div>
						<div class="grid_4 prefix_1">
							<img src="/img/reach_text.png" alt="Reach" /> <br />
							You know what your talking about and you want your audience to understand what you do, so say it without the crutch of jargon or the buzz of buzzwords. Though your buds may think your colorful language is clever, your potential audience might not, so if you want to have a wide reach, keep it clean.

							<li>You used <%= @shout.jargon_num %> buzzwords.</li>


					  	<li>You used <%=h @shout.profanity_num %></span> words that might offend.</li><br />
						</div>
						<div class="grid_1 omega">
							<div class="score">
								<%=h @shout.reach_score %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
						<div class="sep"></div>
					</div>
				<div class="grid_5 prefix_1 alpha">
				<img src="/img/totalscore_text.png" alt="TOTAL SCORE" style="margin-top: 30px;">
				</div>	
				<div class="grid_2 omega">
				<div class="score_total">
					<%=h @shout.total_score %>
					</div>
				</div>
		</div>
		<!-- end .grid_8 -->
		<div class="grid_4">
			<div id="sidebar">
			<h3 class="banner">Most Famous Jumbos</h3>
			<ul>
			<% @famous.each do |fam| %>
				<li>	<a href='/<%=h fam.id %>/show' ><%=h fam.jumbo_name %></a></li>
			<% end %>
			</ul>
			<h3 class="banner_light">Most Recent Jumbos</h3>
			<ul>
			<% @shouts.each do |shout| %>
				<li>
					<a href='/<%=h shout.id %>/show'><%=h shout.jumbo_name %>
					</a>
				</li>
			<% end %>
			</ul>
			<h3 class="banner">High Scorers</h3>
			<ul>
			<% @scores.each do |scorer| %>
				<li>	<a href='/<%=h scorer.id %>/show' ><%=h scorer.jumbo_name %></a></li>
			<% end %>
			</ul>			
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- end .grid_4 -->
		<div class="clear"></div>
		<div class="grid_12">
			<div style="margin: 40px 0px;">
			<span style="color: #044a65;">Created by <a href="http://www.inmans.org" target="_blank">Tim</a> 
			and <a href="http://www.twitter.com/handsomepanda">Jesse Inman</a>.</span>
			</div>
			</div>
		<!-- end .grid_12 -->
	</div>
	<!-- end .container_12 -->

</body>
</html>
